        <num>CC 2541</num>
        <heading>2541.  Reduction of the price</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2541.  Reduction of the price
A buyer may choose to seek only reduction of the price even when the redhibitory defect is such as to give him the right to obtain rescission of the sale.
In an action for rescission because of a redhibitory defect the court may limit the remedy of the buyer to a reduction of the price.</p>
        </content>
